		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.86]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Neptunis&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>Ok a little better info than the other poster.<br><br>Ogre:&nbsp;&nbsp;best Tanking SK, gets slam, better strength but really stupid.  Sentient Armor would over come that but its higher level to get and expensive.  Also if you're going to spend alot of time in dungeons you will learn to hate your size as you will spend a fortune on shrink potions or risk getting stuck.<br><br>Iksar:  Worst faction hits, start in Kunark (good and bad) have a hard time banking in the old world, can't wear plate armors.  Good points, decent Intelligence, regeneration, good quest armors now, superior swimming, forage and good vision.<br><br>Human:  No benefits, can't see, lower Intelligence, lower strength, no slam.  Only good point is they have better faction and can wear Flayed Skin armor.  (Erudins are similar but have the highest Intelligence)<br><br>Trolls:  Slam and Regen, other than that all the size related limitations and dumber than Ogres.<br><br>Dark Elves:  Great vision, can wear medium and small armors (and Plate armor), good newbie area, good Intelligence.  Can't slam, weaker than Ogres/Trolls, fewer hit points but second highest Intelligence, great agility and good dexterity.  <br><br>I think Dark Elves are the best Dungeon Shadow Knights (although Iksars may now be better with the new armors they got) as they easily fit, are easiest to equip with armor and have a high Agility.  Ogres are the best Tanks and can do very well with a Shaman in their group to shrink them.  Dark Elves solo the best from my experience with their higher mana pool.<br><br>Humans offer nothing, Trolls are too stupid and Erudins are too weak to be ballanced Shadow Knights.  <br><br>BEST choices are Dark Elf, Iksar and Ogre.  My opinion is in that order too but at least I explained why.  Iksar may turn out to be the best over-all now, we'll have to see.<br><br>Good Luck whatever you chose.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 45 DE SK</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 62 DE Gravelord<br>Have Axe, will travel</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >2 Replies</td></tr></table><table width="100%"><tr><td class=mhback>&nbsp;</td><td class=mhback >Thread Subject</a></td><td class=mhback>Started by</a></td><td class=mhback>Replies</a></td><td class=mhback>Last Post</a></td><td class=mhback>Rating</a></td></tr><tr class=mdr>
