 end where it be lvl'n quicker, stronger, higher int, regen, nightvision, etc. Now go make ya one of those kickarse sk's and start playing.  You want be disappointed anyway ya go.  <br><br>Zorral (Guildless) lvl 18 sk-Vallon Zek<br><br>DAMN the servers are down again for 9 hrs!!!!<br><br> </p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
